milestones.description: Greenidge has scored 12 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for WI breaking Viv Richards's record
Greenidge has broken the record for most sixes (19) in ODIs for WI, going past Viv Richards's 16
Greenidge has broken the record for most sixes (19) in ODIs, going past Viv Richards's 16
Javed Miandad has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (27) for PAK, going past Wasim Raja
Imran Khan and Wasim Raja's 47-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 37 between Asif Iqbal and Javed Miandad
